fy-Energy-Announces-Third-Quarter-2024-Results-Beta-Drilling-Results-and-Issuance-of-Sustainability-Report/default.aspx\" rel=\"noopener noopener noopener noopener\">report strong results</a> from its new Beta wells. Both its A50 and C59 wells have performed above expectations to date, and it has two more wells to report from its 2024 Beta</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1265591214/image_1265591214.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742494-amplify-energy-ampy-stock-encouraging-results-from-beta-development", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 05:10:00"}, {"id": "4742489", "title": "KCE: A Pre- And Post-Election Winner, Shares Extended (Rating Downgrade)", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/114854593/image_114854593.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Customer signing paperwork with bank manager\" data-id=\"114854593\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/114854593/image_114854593.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/114854593/image_114854593.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/114854593/image_114854593.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/114854593/image_114854593.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/114854593/image_114854593.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/114854593/image_114854593.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/114854593/image_114854593.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/114854593/image_114854593.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw