uploads/getty_images/1073305774/image_1073305774.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1073305774/image_1073305774.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1073305774/image_1073305774.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">StellaMc</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Shares of Zions Bancorporation (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ZION\" title=\"Zions Bancorporation, National Association\">ZION</a></span>) have been a strong performer over the past year, gaining 60%. Its community bank operating model has helped it weather credit volatility and maintain deposit strength, leading to solid financial results. I last covered ZION in July, upgrading</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1073305774/image_1073305774.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742492-zions-bancorporation-strong-underwriting-potential-regulatory-loosening-make-stock-attractive", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 04:49:39"}, {"id": "4742490", "title": "MarketAxess: A Forgotten Stock Worth Buying On The Dip", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/121043904/image_121043904.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Mapping the gains and losses of stock investments\" data-id=\"121043904\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/121043904/image_121043904.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/121043904/image_121043904.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https