ty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2033239552/image_2033239552.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Aerial view of T\u00e4by centrum\" data-id=\"2033239552\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2033239552/image_2033239552.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2033239552/image_2033239552.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2033239552/image_2033239552.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2033239552/image_2033239552.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2033239552/image_2033239552.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2033239552/image_2033239552.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2033239552/image_2033239552.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2033239552/image_2033239552.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Marcus Lindstrom</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><b>Fastighets AB Balder (publ)</b> (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/BALDF\" title=\"Fastighets AB Balder (publ)\">OTCPK:BALDF</a>) is a quality company in the European real estate sector and its business prospects have improved recently, but this seems to be already reflected in its share price.</p> <p>As I've covered in <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/author/labutes-ir/analysis?ticker=BALDF\">previous</a></p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2033239552/image_2033239552.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742478-fastighets-ab-balder-improving-business-prospects-are-priced-in", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 03:39:04"}, {"id": "4742476", "title": "Top 2025 Long Idea: Invest In India With EPI", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1144645520/image_1144645520.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Busy Call Centre in Operation\" data-id=\"1144645520\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1144645520/image_1144645520.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1144645520/image_1144645520.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1144645520/image_1144645520.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1144645520/image_1144645520.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1144645520/image_1144645520.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1144645520/image_1144645520.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1144645520/image_1144645520.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1144645520/image_1144645520.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">GCShutter</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Under the first Donald Trump administration, the U.S.-India relationship was strengthened by increasing trade and cooperation on defense. Going into 2025, India is expected to renew its positive relationship with Trump, capitalizing on the U.S. push away from manufacturing and imports in China. India is</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1144645520/image_1144645520.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742476-top-2025-long-idea-invest-in-india", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 03:20:02"}, {"id": "4742475", "title": "Guidewire Software: Market Expectations Are Stretched Even After Great Q1", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2101979191/image_2101979191.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Pilvipalvelun konsepti. Digitaalinen pilviprosessori emolevyll\u00e4. Tuottavuuden kehitys. Futuristinen pilvikuvake teknologisen kehityksen ja innovaatioiden maailmassa. CGI 3D -render\u00f6inti\" data-id=\"2101979191\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"864px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2101979191/image_2101979191.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2101979191/image_2101979191.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2101979191/image_2101979191.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2101979191/image_2101979191.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2101979191/image_2101979191.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2101979191/image_2101979191.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2101979191/image_2101979191.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2101979191/image_2101979191.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">da-kuk/E+ via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><strong>Guidewire Software, Inc. </strong>(<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/GWRE\" title=\"Guidewire Software, Inc.\">GWRE</a></span>) provides a cloud platform for P&amp;C insurers, including services such as InsuranceSuite, PolicyCenter, BillingCenter, and ClaimCenter \u2013 the company provides very holistic cloud-based services in the industry. As per the </p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2101979191/image_2101979191.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742475-guidewire-software-market-expectations-are-stretched-even-after-great-q1", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 03:06:54"}, {"id": "4742468", "title": "Intuitive Machines Deserves A Spot In Your Portfolio, Just Wait For A Better Entry (Technical Analysis)", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2151535978/image_2151535978.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Successful rocket launch into space on the background of a full moon with craters and stars. Spaceship shuttle lift off into outer space, start of space mission concept\" data-id=\"2151535978\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2151535978/image_2151535978.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2151535978/image_2151535978.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2151535978/image_2151535978.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2151535978/image_2151535978.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w,