han 5% higher on the day, but gave up those gains and then some in Tuesday</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1484082303/image_1484082303.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742238-intel-the-board-shoots-itself-in-the-foot-heres-what-comes-next", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 02:00:00"}]}